Currency Exchange Application
Personal & Business Currency Exchange Platform by Jason Izuchukwu


Project Overview
A Windows Forms application built in C# for secure and efficient currency transfers between personal and business accounts. The system supports multi-currency transactions, scheduled transfers, invoice generation, and administrative oversight.

Target Users

Personal User:	Transfers funds between currency accounts, views exchange rates, tops up balances.
Business User:	Inherits personal features + can schedule transactions, generate invoices, and has higher transfer limits.
System Admin:	Manages user accounts, monitors transactions, unblocks suspended accounts.


Key Features

Personal User
-Create and manage multi-currency accounts
-Transfer funds between own accounts or to external beneficiaries
-View real-time global exchange rates
-Top-up currency accounts from UK bank accounts

Business User

-All personal user features
-Schedule future-dated transactions
-Generate invoices for completed transfers
-Higher transfer limits

System Admin
-View all user accounts and transactions
-Delete or unblock user accounts
-Monitor flagged/suspended transactions


